[33mcommit e031630ce756479c2272538d7b93480526b78ee7[m
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Sat Nov 22 19:08:16 2025 +0000

    Fix backend connection issues and improve reliability
    
    - Move hardcoded backend URLs to app.config for easy configuration
      * Added BackendApiUrl, BackendHealthUrl, StreamlitUrl settings
      * Added ApiTimeoutSeconds, ApiMaxRetries, ApiRetryDelayMs settings
      * Updated ApiClient and QuizPanel to read from configuration
    
    - Add retry logic with exponential backoff for API calls
      * Created RetryAsync helper method with configurable retries
      * Applied retry logic to all API methods (CreateQuiz, StartSession, GetResults, etc.)
      * Exponential backoff: 1s, 2s, 4s delays between retries
      * Improved error messages to indicate retry attempts
    
    - Remove hardcoded file paths from error messages
      * Made backend error message generic and machine-independent
      * Improved user-friendliness of connection error messages
    
    - Add System.Configuration reference to project
      * Required for reading app.config settings

